response.original_title: Ignasi Taltavull – Ya no sé ni lo que digo
response.overview: 'Ya no sé ni lo que digo' is Ignasi Taltavull's new comedy special. An hour of stand-up comedy about love, pigeons, and homosexuality, among other things.  Ignasi Taltavull is a comedian and screenwriter, co-creator of the podcast La Ruina with Tomàs Fuentes, as well as the podcasts Aquí Estamos and Lejos de Aquí with Adri Romeo. He has worked on television programs such as Crackòvia and Està Passant (TV3), and in stand-up comedy, he has directed specials for Magí García and Adri Romeo.
response.title: Ignasi Taltavull – Ya no sé ni lo que digo
